FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://localhost:3000/api/v2

# 📚 Library API

API quản lý thư viện (Books, Members, Loans)

---

# Group Books

## Danh sách sách [/books]

### Lấy danh sách sách [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (array[Book])

---

### Thêm sách [POST]

+ Request (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (BookInput)

+ Response 201 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (Book)

+ Response 400 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (Error)

---

## Chi tiết sách [/books/{id}]

+ Parameters
    + id: `book-123` (string, required)

---

### Lấy chi tiết sách [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (Book)

+ Response 404 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (Error)

---

### Xóa sách [DELETE]

+ Response 204

+ Response 404 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (Error)

---

# Group Members

## Danh sách thành viên [/members]

### Lấy danh sách thành viên [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (array[Member])

---

### Tạo thành viên [POST]

+ Request (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (Member)

+ Response 201 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (Member)

+ Response 400 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (Error)

---

# Group Loans

## Mượn sách [/loans]

### Mượn sách [POST]

+ Request (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (Loan)

+ Response 201 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (Loan)

+ Response 400 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (Error)

---

# Data Structures

## Book (object)
+ id: `book-123` (string)
+ title: `Lập trình Node.js` (string)
+ author: `Nguyễn Văn A` (string)

## BookInput (object)
+ title: `Lập trình Node.js` (string)
+ author: `Nguyễn Văn A` (string)

## Member (object)
+ id: `mem-456` (string)
+ name: `Trần Thị B` (string)

## Loan (object)
+ id: `loan-789` (string)
+ bookId: `book-123` (string)
+ memberId: `mem-456` (string)

## Error (object)
+ message: `Not found` (string)